# Technical Stack Requirements
- Framework: React Router v7 (Remix.run style)
- Language: TypeScript (strict mode)
- React Version: React 19
- Architecture: Epic Stack by Kent C. Dodds

# Code Style Guidelines
## Language
- Code: English only
- UI Text: English only
- Variable names: English, camelCase
- Component names: English, PascalCase

## Documentation
- Comments: Minimal usage
- When needed: JSDoc format only
- Comment language: English only
- Types and interfaces: Well documented

## React Best Practices
- Use React Router data loaders
- Implement Error Boundaries
- Follow React Server Components patterns
- Implement Progressive Enhancement
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Follow Epic Stack conventions

